This should be a plain text file. With a decent text editor, can indent/outdent easily.

Component hierarchy:

• PSF: contains entire app
  • Header: shows logo, user name, button for user details
    • Y: shows user details? or shows user details in modal?
  • Table: shows the user's projects
    • TableHeader: shows the column titles for all projects
    • ExpandableRow: expands to show a project's quotes
      • ProjectInfoRow: shows info for a project
      • Table: shows the project's quotes
        • TableHeader: shows the column titles for all quotes
        • QuoteRow: shows a row for each quote
  • Footer: shows PSF link
